@startuml 网络选课序列图
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #000080
skinparam sequenceActorBackgroundColor #87CEEB

actor 学生 as Student
participant 课程目录 as Catalog
participant 课程 as Course
participant 选课记录 as Selection
participant 支付系统 as Payment
participant 通知服务 as Notification

Student -> Catalog: 查询课程列表()\nout: 课程列表
activate Catalog
Catalog --> Student: return 课程信息数组
deactivate Catalog

Student -> Course: 选择课程(in: 课程ID)\nout: 课程详情
activate Course
Course --> Student: return 课程信息、价格
deactivate Course

alt 付费课程
  Student -> Payment: 支付(in: 学生ID、课程ID、金额)
  activate Payment
  Payment --> Student: return 支付结果
  deactivate Payment
else 免费课程
  Student -> Selection: 创建选课记录(in: 学生ID、课程ID)\nout: 记录ID
  activate Selection
  Selection --> Student: return 选课记录ID
  deactivate Selection
end

Student -> Notification: 发送选课确认邮件(in: 学生邮箱、课程名称)
activate Notification
Notification --> Student: return 邮件发送状态
deactivate Notification

@enduml
